ervices. The company offers business and leisure travel and hospitality services, such as flight bookings; inbound and outbound packaged tours; customized, wildlife, pilgrimage, incentive, and special interest tours; MICE; medical tourism; destination weddings; helicopter and charter flight bookings; luxury trains; cruises; hotel reservations; car and coach hires and rentals; personalized itinerary management; conference and conference management; visa and passport; and travel insurance services. It also owns and operates the Bogmallo Beach Resort, a five-star hotel; and restaurant and banquet facilities. In addition, the company provides foreign exchange services, including foreign currency notes and prepaid Forex international cards, as well as travel education, e-learning, logistics, cargo, and courier services. Further, it is involved in real estate investment, development, and leasing services; and retail spaces. The company was incorporated in 1949 and is based in Navi Mumbai, India. Trade Wings Limited operates as a subsidiary of Narayani Hospitality & Academic Institution Private Limited."}}